name: Soul Star
description:
The soul was wondering through space and time. This life, cosmic live, was so fulfilling, and Soul had no reasons to be relentless. Yet, there was a depth feeling with no real interpretation. 
Soul met a Star and Star sent Soul a message of hope. This was the first time HOPE was felt.
Soul & Star became inseparable from that moment on.
